{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idc9dbf707-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598","identifier":"/us/usc/t43/s422h"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"422h"},"text":"§ 422h.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Planning and construction; transfer of funds","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The planning and construction of projects undertaken pursuant to this subchapter shall be subject to all procedural requirements and other provisions of the Fish and Wildlife Coordination Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/48/401"},"text":"48 Stat. 401","children":[],"tail":"), as amended ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s661"},"text":"16 U.S.C. 661","children":[],"tail":" et seq.). The Secretary shall transfer to the Fish and Wildlife Service or to the National Marine Fisheries Service, out of appropriations or other funds made available under this subchapter, such funds as may be necessary to conduct the investigations required to carry out the purposes of this section."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idc9dbf708-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1956-08-06/ch972/s8"},"text":"Aug. 6, 1956, ch. 972, § 8","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/70/1047"},"text":"70 Stat. 1047","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/553/s1/5"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–553, § 1(5)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1966-09-02"},"text":"Sept. 2, 1966","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/80/377"},"text":"80 Stat. 377","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/546/tIII/s308"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–546, title III, § 308","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1986-10-27"},"text":"Oct. 27, 1986","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/100/3055"},"text":"100 Stat. 3055","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idc9dbf709-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idc9dbf70a-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idc9dbf70b-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Fish and Wildlife Coordination Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/48/401"},"text":"48 Stat. 401","children":[],"tail":"), as amended, referred to in text, is "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1934-03-10/ch55"},"text":"act Mar. 10, 1934, ch. 55","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/48/401"},"text":"48 Stat. 401","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to sections 661 to 666c–1 of Title 16, Conservation. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s661/a"},"text":"section 661(a) of Title 16","children":[],"tail":", Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s661"},"text":"section 661 of Title 16","children":[],"tail":", and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idc9dbf70c-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1986—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/546"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–546","children":[],"tail":" inserted provisions which related to transfer of funds for conduct of investigations to Fish and Wildlife Service or to National Marine Fisheries Service."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1966—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/553"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–553","children":[],"tail":" substituted “the Fish and Wildlife Coordination Act, as amended” for “the Act of "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1946-08-14"},"text":"Aug. 14, 1946","children":[],"tail":" ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/60/1080"},"text":"60 Stat. 1080","children":[],"tail":")”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
